data.description: Well Maintained and Cared For Cape Cod with 4 Bedroom in the Desirable Union Terrace Neighborhood! This property offers two spacious first-floor bedrooms with tons of natural light and a full bath with a linen closet. In the easy-to-finish basement find a finished laundry room and 1/2 bath, a wood-burning stove, and a convenient entrance to the 1-car garage with plenty of off-street parking. A nicely sized wrap-around yard, a full-size shed, in a quiet neighborhood that is still conveniently located close to parks, Markets, and Restaurants.
